<Page x:Class="FitTrack.View.FitTrackInfo"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
      xmlns:local="clr-namespace:FitTrack.View"
      mc:Ignorable="d" 
      d:DesignHeight="450" d:DesignWidth="800"
      Title="FitTrackInfo" Background="LightGray">

    <Grid>
        <StackPanel>
            <TextBlock Text="FitTrack: Your Personalized Fitness Tracker" FontSize="20" Foreground="Crimson" FontWeight="Bold" />
            <TextBlock FontSize="14" >
                FitTrack is a comprehensive fitness app designed to help users easily manage and track their workouts.
                <LineBreak/>
                Whether you're into cardio or strength training, FitTrack offers a streamlined way to log, monitor, and stay consistent with 
                <LineBreak/>
                your fitness goals.
            </TextBlock>
            <Label/>
            <TextBlock Text="Why FitTrack?" FontSize="20" Foreground="Crimson" FontWeight="Bold" />
            <TextBlock FontSize="14">
                FitTrack is designed to help users maintain a clear overview of their fitness progress. By focusing on ease of use, security, 
                <LineBreak/>
                and flexibility, FitTrack empowers users to log detailed information about their workouts, making it simple to track 
                <LineBreak/> 
                improvements over time. 
                <LineBreak/> 
                <LineBreak/> 
                Stay consistent, stay organized, and take control of your fitness journey with FitTrack!

            </TextBlock>
        </StackPanel>
    </Grid>
</Page>
